OL,3,CReform pledge to scrap benefits for
OL,4,Cpeople with 'non-serious anxiety'
OL,6,FReform UK have promised to scrap
OL,7,Fpersonal independence payments (Pip)
OL,8,Fif elected, for claimants with "non-
OL,9,Fserious anxiety disorders" and
OL,10,Fintroduce more regular reassessments
OL,11,Ffor those who qualify.
OL,13,FThe proposal is one of several aimed
OL,14,Fat reforming the welfare system, which
OL,15,Falso include increasing the amount of
OL,16,Fface-to-face assessments and
OL,17,Fintroducing a "fast track to work"
OL,18,Fsystem for those having their payments
OL,19,Fwithdrawn.
