OL,6,FSpeaking at a press conference on
OL,7,FWednesday, Zia Yusuf described young
OL,8,Fpeople on disability benefits as being
OL,9,F"tossed onto a scrap heap," saying:
OL,10,F"The caseload for new claims for under-
OL,11,F25s in this country on Pip have
OL,12,Ftripled in five years.
OL,14,F"So we are betraying our young people.
OL,15,FReassessments are basically not
OL,16,Fhappening anymore. These young people
OL,17,Fare... being basically tossed onto a
OL,18,Fscrap heap for the rest of their
OL,19,Flives."
