OL,6,FPushed on what withdrawing support for
OL,7,Fpeople with anxiety would mean for
OL,8,Fthose claimants' lives, Anderson
OL,9,Fclaimed returning to work was the best
OL,10,Ftreatment for them.
OL,12,FTurning to his own experiences, he
OL,13,Fsaid: "When I worked down the pit it
OL,14,Fwas dangerous, it was dark, it was
OL,15,Fdirty and sometimes we were worried.
OL,17,F"But the following morning at 5 o
OL,18,Fclock we went back to work again -
OL,19,Fthat was the best medication I've ever
OL,20,Fhad."
